# CVEs in pre-compiled Go binaries bundled inside infrastructure-bundle.
# These binaries (newrelic-infra, nri-*) are not built here; fixes require
# a new infrastructure-bundle release with an updated agent/integrations build.
# Track: https://github.com/newrelic/infrastructure-bundle

# stdlib: mime/multipart header parsing (fixed in Go 1.26.4)
CVE-2026-42504

# containerd: CVE affecting containerd in newrelic-infra (fixed in containerd 1.7.33)
CVE-2026-53488
